#: of numpy.nanmin:50
msgid ""
"An array with the same shape as `a`, with the specified axis removed.  If "
"`a` is a 0-d array, or if axis is None, an ndarray scalar is returned.  The "
"same dtype as `a` is returned."
msgstr ""

